    <h1>JSPUI Configuration and Customization</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>The DSpace digital repository supports two user interfaces: one =
based on JavaServer Pages (JSP) technologies and one based upon the Apache =
Cocoon framework (XMLUI). This chapter describes those parameters which are=
 specific to the JPSUI interface.</p>=20
